Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，這樣就全搬完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有忘了東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了和清水老師一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保搬家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.45,0:01:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.69,0:02:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#21         ちぃ，回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誘拐事件也已落幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回到了日常的作息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是跟以前一樣去補習班上課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去「樂意之至」打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.88,0:02:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然看起來跟以往一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.21,0:02:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事卻漸漸地變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ又開始到奇洛如去打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿什麼也沒發生過似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高高興興的去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿什麼也沒發生過似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題，沒有忘記拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.62,0:03:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，有些事不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要知道更清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要壓我的頭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴子果然跟絲茉茉差不多高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，絲茉茉身高16公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，我是本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在過去你那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹要出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.13,0:03:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.76,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打工很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼而快樂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹會高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不是說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說打工這件事快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起打工\Nちぃ比較喜歡現在這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟秀樹在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對電腦雖然不是很懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過所謂的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對電腦來說\N是很特別的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.63,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說前任主人的程式還留著呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目的地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉的地圖資料裡有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是國分寺稔的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次來都覺得很驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在很忙走不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法下去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你自己進來我的書房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡竟然還有廣播系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意腳下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在查事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，在你正忙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不放心她一個人在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後還有發生什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬也休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正試著整理\N之前找到的關於ちぃ的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳待機時不能更安靜點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的程式就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.61,0:06:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於ちぃ是什麼樣的電腦\N一無所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前覺得這樣也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果ちぃ又發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ又遇到什麼意外的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想搞清楚ちぃ的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想盡力幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這東西的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我整理出的資料推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得Chobits的開發計劃中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有某些內幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內幕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些內容\N還是跟都市傳說脫不了關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就姑且聽聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,號稱終極電腦的Chobits系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎跟某個組織有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初開始製造電腦的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的開發者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和身為客戶的組織之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎發生理念不合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於組織不斷的干涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發者開始感到不快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發者瞞著組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造出特別的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許對那個組織來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一件對他們相當不利的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，那部份我還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.09,0:07:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我輕率的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會引發上次那種誘拐事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想幫你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不止這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿茶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做家事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為系統正在使用女傭電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬才是系統的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候要休息才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我自己來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.92,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說只要睡一晚就能康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然累到昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說最近他幾乎沒睡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我拜託他調查才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是本須和少爺的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都要怪我的性能不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.15,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的處理速度能更快一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會給稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶來這麼大的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能更有用一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有方法能辦得到的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是沒有方法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來討皮痛的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.61,0:09:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然還有臉到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是M拜託我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要跟我借電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺拜託他幫忙調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.96,0:09:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為小島少爺\N電腦方面的知識也很豐富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事我也覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點太入迷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的辦法是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.97,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過了關於\N開發Chobits組織的故事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最快的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是駭那個組織的主電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有需要生氣嗎，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂駭客就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於自己沒有使用權限的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行非法侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說就是電腦內的竊聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事做得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上已經找到目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險？什麼樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方不是普通的伺服器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然會準備\N各種的防禦程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能會當機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂當機就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料或記憶消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.96,0:10:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更嚴重一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個硬碟都可能無法使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就行不通了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓柚姬做這種事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人這麼說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且M也不贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經建議過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭賭看讓妳試著去入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢再說一次試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不輕饒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是最有效率的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我絕對不能讓柚姬做那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.40,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誘人的情報明明就掛在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M卻不肯動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬對稔來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是電腦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不用這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只能一直繞遠路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕哪天他又會倒下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讓稔輕鬆一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你加倍努力就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我比以前更努力兩三倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免你偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來監視你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上我不回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也擔心稔的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作室在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去，我會去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你設計讓我只會說實話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做，我做就是了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，應該說大部份電腦不會說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.05,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們是被這麼設計的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剛剛柚姬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能更有用一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹叫我來看看情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是稔少爺的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是柚姬嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟姊姊不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是照姊姊的模樣製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且輸入各種姊姊的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.36,0:13:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我跟姊姊還是不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的姊姊一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以幫稔少爺更多的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.11,0:14:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ如果想幫本須和忙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會願意為他做任何事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.88,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是做會讓自己壞掉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹快樂，ちぃ也會很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.56,0:14:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果秀樹會快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ會做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的樣子也怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電力這麼不安定的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會影響作業的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連到屋子的安全系統看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.07,0:14:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子的電力都集中到一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在使用書房的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書房？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了會是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.35,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人侵入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，穿過我們的防禦系統進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是台性能相當好的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來連接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔，你在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說過不可以勉強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰在使用這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能使用這裡的系統的\N除了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在裡面對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，妳在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼柚姬要瞞著稔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在用房子裡的廣播系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在侵入小島找到的\N那個組織的伺服器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.31,0:16:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在解析第五層密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手，太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.68,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便解除的話\N是會啟動防禦程式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法了解稔少爺的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道這是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.79,0:16:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但稔少爺仍因為考慮到我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果是真的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定就可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬妳在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說這種話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.34,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，妳在說什麼啊，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為輸入了姊姊的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為真的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己變成怎樣都沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是程式設定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那實在太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像姊姊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫稔少爺的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳弄錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳弄錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬不是姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解析完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始下載資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門鎖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕人的手段真是粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不准任何人侵入吉瑪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好像在吃醋一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.21,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明都只是電腦說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.86,0:18:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我徹底檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前看來沒什麼重大的故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好這個先燒斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己掃瞄看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一部份資料受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關於姊姊的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再輸入姊姊的資料給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他部份呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為記憶區塊不同\N所以沒有受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不輸入姊姊的資料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.88,0:19:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法接受這個事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘記姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，應該說是不想忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以製造了柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能做得像是\N我記憶中的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是柚姬不是姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我太沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能取代姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也沒人能取代柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能取代我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我只是電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是在我看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬跟其他的電腦不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是程式設計出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬就是柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再輸入姊姊的資料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟姊姊一起的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是重要的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是柚姬陪伴我的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我重要的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今後也想繼續創造下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是代替姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是跟柚姬在一起的重要時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累積好多好多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不能代替姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以待在稔少爺身邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要柚姬在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.47,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬看起來好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.68,0:20:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，回憶是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是指\N留在心中的重要東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不是像資料那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠輕易替換的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ和秀樹也有回憶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.83,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.97,0:21:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像資料那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠輕易替換的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔，你已經沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你帶來了不少麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.85,0:21:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來\N都是因為我硬要你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.12,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會繼續調查下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過別太勉強自己喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.89,0:21:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬剛剛下載的資料一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後會仔細調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.50,0:21:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦開發者的名單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.41,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也有圖片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可能會嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.25,0:21:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發人員中的靈魂人物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.18,0:22:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.49,0:22:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.46,0:23:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.15,0:23:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.56,0:23:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.63,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.21,0:23:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹什麼時候最幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.13,0:23:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一堆好吃東西的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.43,0:23:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班考試得到好成績的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽手的時候呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽手的時候也很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼問這個問題呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.34,0:24:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.08,0:24:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.61,0:24:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits下一回\N「ちぃ，更衣」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要牽起手來，大家都會幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
